move1.name: Rock Throw
move1.description: The user throws rocks at the target to inflict damage.

move2.name: Iron Tail
move2.description: The target is slammed with a steel-hard tail. It may also lower the target's Defense stat.

move3.name: Rock Slide
move3.description: Large boulders are hurled at the opposing team to inflict damage. It may also make the targets flinch.

move4.name: Stone Edge
move4.description: The user stabs the target from below with sharpened stones. Critical hits land more easily.
